<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
  <title>여의명상센터 — 한울사상</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+KR:wght@200;300;400;600&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@200;300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html, body { height: 100%; font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif; background: #0D0D0D; color: #F0EDE6; overflow-x: hidden; }

    /* ─── SIDE NAV ─────────────────────────────────── */
    .sidenav {
      position: fixed; left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 72px;
      background: rgba(13,13,13,0.92);
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
      padding: 2rem 0;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .sidenav-logo {
      writing-mode: vertical-rl; text-orientation: mixed;
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      color: rgba(240,237,230,0.5);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .sidenav-line { width: 1px; flex: 1; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
    .sidenav-links {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 1.6rem;
    }
    .sidenav-links a {
      writing-mode: vertical-rl;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 200;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      color: rgba(240,237,230,0.35);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    .sidenav-links a:hover { color: rgba(240,237,230,0.9); }

    /* ─── MAIN LAYOUT ───────────────────────────────── */
    .layout { margin-left: 72px; }

    /* ─── HERO SPLIT ────────────────────────────────── */
    .hero-split {
      height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
    .hero-img {
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-img img {
      width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;
      filter: brightness(0.7) saturate(0.8);
      transition: transform 8s ease;
    }
    .hero-img:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }
    .hero-img-overlay {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(13,13,13,0.3) 0%, rgba(13,13,13,0.05) 100%);
    }
    .hero-img-label {
      position: absolute; bottom: 2rem; left: 2rem;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 200;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      color: rgba(240,237,230,0.5);
    }

    .hero-text {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
      padding: 6vw;
      background: #0D0D0D;
      position: relative;
    }
    .hero-text::before {
      content: '韓蔚';
      position: absolute; top: 50%; right: -0.1em;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      font-size: 18rem; font-weight: 200;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
      line-height: 1;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero-tag {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 200;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      color: rgba(180,155,110,0.8);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .hero-title {
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
      font-weight: 200;
      line-height: 1.3;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: #F0EDE6;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .hero-title em { font-style: normal; color: rgba(180,155,110,0.9); }
    .hero-desc {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 200;
      line-height: 2.2;
      color: rgba(240,237,230,0.5);
      max-width: 360px;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .hero-cta {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      color: rgba(240,237,230,0.7);
      text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(240,237,230,0.2);
      padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      width: fit-content;
    }
    .hero-cta:hover { color: #F0EDE6; border-bottom-color: rgba(180,155,110,0.8); }
    .hero-cta::after { content: '→'; font-size: 0.8rem; }

    /* ─── PHOTO STRIP ────────────────────────────────── */
    .photo-strip {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      height: 40vh;
    }
    .photo-strip-item {
      overflow: hidden; position: relative; cursor: pointer;
    }
    .photo-strip-item img {
      width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;
      transition: transform 0.8s ease, filter 0.8s ease;
      filter: brightness(0.6) saturate(0.6);
    }
    .photo-strip-item:hover img {
      transform: scale(1.1);
      filter: brightness(0.8) saturate(0.9);
    }
    .photo-strip-item .label {
      position: absolute; bottom: 1.2rem; left: 1.2rem;
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 300;
      color: rgba(240,237,230,0.85);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }
    .photo-strip-item .sublabel {
      position: absolute; bottom: 0.5rem; left: 1.2rem;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.55rem; font-weight: 200;
      color: rgba(240,237,230,0.4);
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    }

    /* ─── TEACHING SECTION ──────────────────────────── */
    .teaching {
      padding: 12vh 8vw;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
      gap: 8vw;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .teaching-label {
      position: sticky; top: 30vh;
    }
    .teaching-num {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: 4rem; font-weight: 200;
      color: rgba(180,155,110,0.15);
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .teaching-title {
      font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 300;
      color: rgba(240,237,230,0.8);
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    }
    .teaching-items { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5vh; }
    .teaching-item {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      padding-top: 3vh;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr; gap: 2rem;
    }
    .teaching-hanja {
      font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 200;
      color: rgba(180,155,110,0.6);
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .teaching-content h3 {
      font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 300;
      color: rgba(240,237,230,0.85);
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }
    .teaching-content p {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 200;
      color: rgba(240,237,230,0.45);
      line-height: 2.0;
    }

    /* ─── QUOTE BREAK ────────────────────────────────── */
    .quote-break {
      padding: 12vh 0;
      background: rgba(180,155,110,0.05);
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(180,155,110,0.1);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(180,155,110,0.1);
    }
    .quote-mark {
      font-size: 4rem; font-weight: 200;
      color: rgba(180,155,110,0.2);
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .quote-text {
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.4rem);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 2.2;
      color: rgba(240,237,230,0.75);
      max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }
    .quote-src {
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 200;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      color: rgba(180,155,110,0.5);
    }

    /* ─── FOOTER ─────────────────────────────────────── */
    .footer {
      padding: 6vh 8vw;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .footer-logo {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      color: rgba(240,237,230,0.3);
    }
    .footer-info {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 200;
      color: rgba(240,237,230,0.2);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-align: right;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- 사이드 내비게이션 -->
<nav class="sidenav">
  <a class="sidenav-logo" href="/">여의명상센터</a>
  <div class="sidenav-line"></div>
  <div class="sidenav-links">
    <a href="#">사상</a>
    <a href="#">수행</a>
    <a href="#">법회</a>
    <a href="#">갤러리</a>
    <a href="#">안내</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="layout">

  <!-- 히어로 스플릿 -->
  <section class="hero-split">
    <div class="hero-img">
      <img src="/api/img-proxy?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcafeptthumb-phinf.pstatic.net%2FMjAyNDEwMTdfOTQg%2FMDAxNzI5MDk5MjQ3OTUw.NV6HuuzljMwmzWraMA2WXY7cSoeYetEglnn2SflszQcg.a6gNojQAJe9-5Dhfr-HbJ5y9q1HNo8cFBvs7JgWe49Eg.JPEG%2F20241013%EF%BC%BF153757.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw1600" alt="여의명상센터">
      <div class="hero-img-overlay"></div>
      <span class="hero-img-label">여의명상센터 — 2024</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-text">
      <p class="hero-tag">YEOUIMYEONGSANG CENTER</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">한울사상<br><em>韓蔚思想</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">하늘과 땅이 하나임을 깨달아<br>인간 본래의 빛을 회복하는<br>깊은 수행의 길</p>
      <a class="hero-cta" href="#">사상 알아보기</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 사진 띠 -->
  <section class="photo-strip">
    <div class="photo-strip-item">
      <img src="/api/img-proxy?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcafeptthumb-phinf.pstatic.net%2FMjAyNDEwMTdfNTEg%2FMDAxNzI5MDk5MjQzOTA5.0SkIpLW56bh2MeWz4ECADciWjs4j-O7rojMrQjtJ5XYg.pHNYccP_2XO03LuLPv1gmmHmqoA9pVpykLtkyAvZ8Ycg.JPEG%2F20241013%EF%BC%BF153749.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw1600" alt="">
      <span class="label">한울의 빛</span>
      <span class="sublabel">HANUL LIGHT</span>
    </div>
    <div class="photo-strip-item">
      <img src="/api/img-proxy?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcafeptthumb-phinf.pstatic.net%2FMjAyMDEwMjhfOCAg%2FMDAxNjAzODY3OTk2MzYx.UrzBhXUixJQB7ccIBtG9Vafs8Y1PCZoBpwF-aB8Yzd0g.Fh9fgRSD2sm5BUxSIpVNwSL8SJaxrs5H8sEA7wdS1pgg.JPEG%2F1_%282%29.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw1600" alt="">
      <span class="label">기운영</span>
      <span class="sublabel">ENERGY PRACTICE</span>
    </div>
    <div class="photo-strip-item">
      <img src="/api/img-proxy?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcafeptthumb-phinf.pstatic.net%2FMjAyNDA4MTBfMjE0%2FMDAxNzIzMjk3NTUzMzY4.1qbz4B5bjM0YfcSxEP1RgMsP3KGZ2jAGcuunFzEQ3nUg.zjzmmi1fqgeecnxsf0IqmZ_2bhPQvcelYAA26CWZOjwg.JPEG%2F20240810%EF%BC%BF222724.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw1600" alt="">
      <span class="label">수행 법회</span>
      <span class="sublabel">DHARMA ASSEMBLY</span>
    </div>
    <div class="photo-strip-item">
      <img src="/api/img-proxy?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcafeptthumb-phinf.pstatic.net%2FMjAyMzExMDlfMTk2%2FMDAxNjk5NTI2MDExNDQ5.VYp2R73bemNcLZGDMJoPS49ZWIeiWEBTRetNkQe6gcEg.iWZ7MQIleuFMzTAkOABYBvYm-r4FrOW_5aIC5_Sd-C0g.JPEG%2F20231102_113534.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw1600" alt="">
      <span class="label">지기 답사</span>
      <span class="sublabel">CULTURE JOURNEY</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 가르침 섹션 -->
  <section class="teaching">
    <div class="teaching-label">
      <div class="teaching-num">01</div>
      <div class="teaching-title">핵심<br>사상</div>
    </div>
    <div class="teaching-items">
      <div class="teaching-item">
        <div class="teaching-hanja">天</div>
        <div class="teaching-content">
          <h3>한울 — 하늘의 근원</h3>
          <p>한울은 하늘과 우리의 고유어로, 무한한 우주적 생명 에너지를 의미합니다. 모든 존재는 이 한울의 기운 안에서 태어나고 돌아갑니다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="teaching-item">
        <div class="teaching-hanja">氣</div>
        <div class="teaching-content">
          <h3>기 — 생명의 에너지</h3>
          <p>눈에 보이지 않으나 만물을 움직이는 근원적 힘. 수행을 통해 이 기운을 깨워 몸과 마음의 균형을 회복합니다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="teaching-item">
        <div class="teaching-hanja">道</div>
        <div class="teaching-content">
          <h3>도 — 수행의 길</h3>
          <p>여의명상과 기운영을 통해 깊은 내면과 연결되고, 하늘의 뜻을 몸으로 실천하는 살아있는 수도의 여정입니다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 인용 -->
  <section class="quote-break">
    <div class="quote-mark">"</div>
    <p class="quote-text">우리는 하늘과 땅이 어울려서, 천지(天地)가 어울려서 생긴 존재들입니다.<br>그 근원을 기억하고 회복하는 것이 수행의 본질입니다.</p>
    <p class="quote-src">— 한울수도법 서문</p>
  </section>

  <!-- 푸터 -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer-logo">여의명상센터</div>
    <div class="footer-info">
      한울사상 아카이브<br>
      cafe.naver.com/zerofield
    </div>
  </footer>

</div>
</body>
</html>
